com.blockwithme.util.server

Class LongObjectCacheImpl<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.ref.ReferenceQueue<E>
      • com.blockwithme.util.server.LongObjectCacheImpl<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LongObjectCache<E>

    public class LongObjectCacheImpl<E>
extends ReferenceQueue<E>
implements LongObjectCache<E>
    Weak object cache, where each object has a unique, immutable long ID. No hard reference is kept for the object, therefore allowing GC. Long are no good as IDs in GWT.
    Author:
    monster
